  "narration": {
    "text": "This is your Coordinator Dashboard. The control room for everything moving through the pipeline. Right at the center, Suggested Tasks — fresh work waiting for someone to claim. Each card shows size, priority, and deadline so you can triage at a glance. To grab one, just hit Pick Up — one click and it's yours. Over in the sidebar, your Coordinator Queue is calling — nine items need your call right now. Below that, Review Submissions collects drafts ready for your eyes. The status strip up top gives you the team pulse — Approved, On Hold, in motion. From here you can jump into Block Health, the Team Board, or Project Tracker any time. This is home base — start your day here.",
